T02TD3096E:189a-1: a'arya ta th'a ga toshn'i sha si t'a ta pa tre n'a ma dh'a ra ni bidhi n'a ma /
T02TD3096E:189a-3: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor nas byung ba'i gdugs dkar mo can zhes bya ba'i gzungs kyi cho ga zhes bya ba /
T02TD3096E:189a-4: 'phags ma gdugs dkar mo can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3096E:189a-5: rnal 'byor nus pa chung gyur zhing //
T02TD3096E:189a-6: bsdus pa la mos sems can la //
T02TD3096E:189a-7: tsanda bdag gis legs bsdus te //
T02TD3096E:189a-8: gzungs kyi cho ga dgod par bya //
T02TD3096E:189a-9: dang por sngags pa dam tshig ldan //
T02TD3096E:189a-10: byang chub sems ldan rab sbyangs te //
T02TD3096E:189a-11: cho ga bsdus rgyas mkhas pa yis //
T02TD3096E:189a-12: manda la chag chag btab steng du //
T02TD3096E:189a-13: dri yi byug pa legs bsgos te //
T02TD3096E:189a-14: dang por dbus su padma ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-0: 'dab brgyad ge sar @189b bcas pa bri //
T02TD3096E:189b-1: de yi phyir ni bcu drug pa //
T02TD3096E:189b-2: bris te sgo ni gcig pa bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-3: de dbus rin chen khri stang du //
T02TD3096E:189b-4: bum pa mtshan nyid ldan ba gzhag / rgyan dang dri yi sa chus gang bya'o //
T02TD3096E:189b-5: de nas mchod dang gtor ma bsham //
T02TD3096E:189b-6: dang po byang chub sems bskyed la //
T02TD3096E:189b-7: bdun po rnam par dag pa yi //
T02TD3096E:189b-8: sngon 'gros lha mo bskyed par bya'o //
T02TD3096E:189b-9: de nas bzlas dang gtor ma dang //
T02TD3096E:189b-10: mchod dang bstod pa la sogs bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-11: bum pa mi dmigs bhr'um las ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-12: rin chen las grub gzhal yas khang //
T02TD3096E:189b-13: dkyil 'khor cho ga nas gsungs pa //
T02TD3096E:189b-14: rin pas bskyed pa rdzogs par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-15: byin brlabs ye shes spyan drang dang //
T02TD3096E:189b-16: de rjes mchod pas mchod par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-17: bstod dang gsol gdab bzlas pa bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-19: tshur 'dus bdag gi sdig pa dag / ngo bo chu la rnam pa lnga //
T02TD3096E:189b-20: yang na bzlog pa'i rnam par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-21: de nas legs ldan chen po la //
T02TD3096E:189b-22: gtor ma rgyas par byin nas ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-23: slob ma khrus byas stan la 'dug thun mong khyad bar sdom pa kun //
T02TD3096E:189b-24: phog la lha la mchod bstod bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-25: de nas thams cad 'joms pa yi //
T02TD3096E:189b-26: sngags kyis slob ma bsrung bskrad la //
T02TD3096E:189b-27: de nas bum pa'i chu yis ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-28: slob ma'i mgo nas blugs pa dang //
T02TD3096E:189b-29: bkra shis tshigs bcad brjod par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-30: sdig sgrib dag ste rang gi ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-31: rigs kyis dbu la brgyan par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-32: de nas me tog mchod pa dang //
T02TD3096E:189b-33: dbu rgyan la sogs byas de nas //
T02TD3096E:189b-34: rang gi 'dod don gsol ba gdab //
T02TD3096E:189b-35: bla ma la ni yon phul la //
T02TD3096E:189b-36: rang gi dam tshig brjod par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-37: bla mas dkyil 'khor la srung ba'i //
T02TD3096E:189b-38: dam tshig rgyas par bsgrags nas ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-39: byung bsal la sogs rdzogs par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-40: de nas srung ba'i 'khor lo yang //
T02TD3096E:189b-41: cho ga ltar bris bsngags par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-43: byas te gong ltar cho ga bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-44: shin tu bsdus la bum par ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-45: lha mo nyid sku rdzogs par ni //
T02TD3096E:189b-46: byas te smon lam la sogs bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-47: de nas khrus sogs rgyas par bya //
T02TD3096E:189b-48: des ni phyi nang gnod pa dang //
T02TD3096E:189b-49: sdig pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus pa //
T02TD3096E:189b-50: thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ba yin //
T02TD3096E:189b-51: gzhan yang las tshogs ma lus pa //
T02TD3096E:190a-2: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor nas byung ba'i gdugs dkar mo can gyi cho ga'i man ngag / slob dpon tsandra go mis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3096E:190a-4: // / bla ma zangs dkar lo ts'a bas bsgyur ba'o//
